192
00:12:32,509 --> 00:12:34,409
Na Joong Rye.

193
00:12:34,409 --> 00:12:35,509
Tunggu.

194
00:12:36,080 --> 00:12:39,779
Aku Kim Gan Nan. Siapa namamu?

195
00:12:39,779 --> 00:12:42,620
Aku tidak perlu memberi tahu namaku.

196
00:12:42,620 --> 00:12:43,779
Aku tutup sekarang.

197
00:12:43,779 --> 00:12:45,750
Jangan begitu.

198
00:12:45,750 --> 00:12:49,460
Dengarkan aku.

199
00:12:49,460 --> 00:12:52,590
Aku sudah lama tinggal di dekat Jak Doo.

200
00:12:52,590 --> 00:12:56,460
Jadi, dia seperti putraku sendiri.

201
00:12:56,529 --> 00:12:59,370
Jadi, bagi Jak Doo,

202
00:12:59,399 --> 00:13:01,399
kami seperti ibunya.

203
00:13:01,399 --> 00:13:03,700
Kamu adalah ibu dari istrinya,

204
00:13:03,700 --> 00:13:05,909
yang sifatnya seperti ibu tiri.

205
00:13:05,909 --> 00:13:08,679
Ibu tiri? Beraninya kamu.

206
00:13:08,679 --> 00:13:12,480
Tunggu! Bukan, maksudku

207
