215
00:13:31,059 --> 00:13:34,269
Astaga, jangan begitu. Dia ibu mertuanya.

216
00:13:34,269 --> 00:13:36,899
Jangan kasar kepadanya.

217
00:13:37,940 --> 00:13:41,509
Tampaknya suasana hati kita sedang tidak bagus.

218
00:13:41,509 --> 00:13:44,080
